Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:02:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}古都 黑兔回忆录
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖 别哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们肯定会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这就结束了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊 谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}曾经在某地 有位拥有神奇力量的和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他所画的画就像有生命一般 能自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}人们都觉得毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}和尚越来越难以跟别人相处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}于是他就孤身一人 安静地躲在山中过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:09.20,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I think of how it all was made
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我思考着这一切是如何被创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:15.93,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Each detail of this world portrayed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}描写了这世界每一个细节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:22.31,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}In bursts of color, every sight and sound
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}连接出现的无数色彩 一切的景象和声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:29.28,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The wide blue sky and the immobile ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还有广阔的蓝天与稳固的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:36.57,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all too great to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这一切伟大得让人难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:43.07,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The moon, with one stroke of his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在他着下一笔后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:49.74,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Started to glow and all the stars appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明月开始发出光亮 并出现众多繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:56.06,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How did it all end up here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这奇迹究竟如何产生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:03.47,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I am here at this crucial time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在关键时刻来到此处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:11.19,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hope I find what I came to find
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望我能找到我来找寻的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:17.04,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm destined to be, the way I'm meant to be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是注定好的 也是必须发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:23.08,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have to find my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我一定要找到我路
