Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:36.81,eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Learn to love and always seek for what is right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}学懂去爱 与永能找出正确的事
